---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

import Card from '../../layouts/Card.astro';
import InfoColumn from '../../components/InfoColumn.astro';
---
<Card title="Accessibility audits" metaDescription="I offer various accessibility services to teams of, for example, content editors, designers or developers">
  <section class="text-center space-y-4">
    <h1>Accessibility Audits</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-left">Each package can be tailored to better suit the needs of your website. The pricing will be adjusted based on the changes.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-left">If none of the predefined packages suit your needs, a fully tailored audit is the most cost-effective. Reach out and let's discuss your needs in more detail.</p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="services-title">
    <span id="services-title" class="sr-only">The services I offer</span>
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <article class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume flex items-center">Light</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Approximately 10 pages tested manually.</li>
              <li>Automated testing up to 500 pages.</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Suitable for:
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Small sites with less than five different types of content</li>
              <li>Sites that need a quick check into accessibility to get started</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Price: 2 475 € + VAT</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume flex items-center">Standard</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Approximately 12 pages tested manually.</li>
              <li>Automated testing up to 1000 pages.</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Suitable for:
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Small and medium content-heavy websites</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Price: 3 300 € + VAT</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume flex items-center">Advanced</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Approximately 24 pages tested manually.</li>
              <li>Automated testing up to 2000 pages.</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Suitable for:
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Smaller websites for more extensive look on accessibility</li>
              <li>Medium websites</li>
              <li>Large content-heavy websites</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Price: 4 950 € + VAT</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume flex items-center">Comprehensive</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Approximately 36 pages tested manually.</li>
              <li>Automated testing up to 3000 pages.</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Suitable for:
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Medium and larger websites</li>
              <li>Small and medium e-commerce sites. (With e-commerce websites the most suitable audit package depends on the type of shop and its features.)</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Price: 6 500 € + VAT</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="me" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20">
    <h2 id="content" class="font-bold text-xl text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume">What you get from the audit?</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3 mt-4">
      <InfoColumn icon="user-group"
        description="The audit will not only focus on compliance with WCAG 2.2 standards but also consider the overall user experience for individuals with disabilities. This holistic approach ensures that your website is not only legally compliant but also genuinely accessible and user-friendly."
      />
      <InfoColumn icon="wrench-screwdriver"
        description="The report will provide you with a clear understanding of your website's accessibility status, highlighting both strengths and areas for improvement. Each issue will be accompanied by practical recommendations to help your team implement necessary changes."
      />
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 ">
        <Icon name="list-bullet" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">The audit in a nutshell:
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Testing with 2 screen readers (by default Windows NVDA, iPhone VoiceOver)</li>
              <li>Automated testing with <a href="https://webwarden.com" class="underline hover:no-underline">Webwarden</a></li>
              <li>Accessibility expert testing, feedback and suggestions</li>
              <li>Comprehensive report detailing found issues and remedies for them</li>
              <li>Accessibility and usability findings also outside of the legal scope</li>
              <li>Meeting together with the auditor to through the results</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="me" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20">
    <h2 id="options" class="font-bold text-xl text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume">Extra options</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3 mt-4">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 ">
        <Icon name="academic-cap" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              Accessibility statement creation or update based on audit findings.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
              The accessibility statement can be provided in Finnish or English. If you need both, let me know!
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
              Don't know what an accessibility statement is? <a href="https://a11y.ing/en/fundamentals/the-basics/accessibility-statement/" class="underline hover:no-underline">Learn about accessibility statements</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
            Price: 590 € + VAT
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 ">
        <Icon name="computer-desktop" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              Testing on more screen readers:
              <ul class=" text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-4">
                <li>Android TalkBack</li>
                <li>VoiceOver (MacOS)</li>
                <li>JAWS</li>
              </ul>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
              We can increase test coverage by adding more screen readers.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
              NB! If you'd prefer, the default two screen readers can be replaced with any of the above.
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
            Price: 300 € + VAT per screen reader
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 ">
        <Icon name="presentation-chart-line" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
          <div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              Role-based accessibility training based on the audit findings (1 hour, remote).
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
              The training can be organized for:
              <ul class=" text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-4">
                <li>content editors</li>
                <li>designers</li>
                <li>developers</li>
              </ul>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
              The training can be more theoretical or we can practice with real examples from your website and get the fixing process started.
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6 justify-end">
            Price: 500 € + VAT
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="text-center space-y-4">
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Interested in working together?</p>
    <a href="mailto:sanna@a11y.ing" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-dk-purple-header dark:bg-lt-perfume text-white dark:text-black font-medium hover:opacity-90">Contact me</a>
  </section>
</Card>